  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0001",
          "zh": "卷六十四 志第四十",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0002",
          "zh": "◎儀衛 《周官》，王之儀衛分掌於天官、春官、夏官之屬，而蹕事則專屬於秋官。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0003",
          "zh": "漢朝會，則衛官陳車騎，張旗幟。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0004",
          "zh": "唐沿隋制，置衛尉卿，掌儀仗帳幕之事。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0005",
          "zh": "宋衛 尉領左右金吾衛司、左右金吾仗司、六軍儀仗司，主清道、徼巡、排列、奉引儀 仗。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0006",
          "zh": "元置拱衛司，領控鶴戶以供其事。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0007",
          "zh": "歷代制度雖有沿革異同，總以謹出入之防， 嚴尊卑之分。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0008",
          "zh": "慎重則尊嚴，尊嚴則整肅，是故文謂之儀，武謂之衛。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0009",
          "zh": "天子出，車 駕次第謂之鹵簿。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0010",
          "zh": "而唐制四品以上皆給鹵簿，則君臣並得通稱也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0011",
          "zh": "明初詔禮官， 鹵簿彌文，務從省節，以示尚質去奢之意。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0012",
          "zh": "凡正、至、聖節、朝會，及冊拜、接 見蕃臣，儀鸞司陳設儀仗。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0013",
          "zh": "而中宮、東宮、親王皆有儀仗之制。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0014",
          "zh": "後或隨時增飾， 要以洪武創制爲準則焉。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0015",
          "zh": "茲撮《集禮》所載大凡，以備考覈。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0016",
          "zh": "其郡王及皇妃、東 宮妃以下儀仗，載在《會典》者，並著於篇云。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0017",
          "zh": "皇帝儀仗：吳元年十二月辛酉，中書左相國李善長率禮官以即位禮儀進。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0018",
          "zh": "是 日清晨，拱衛司陳設鹵簿，列甲士於午門外之東西，列旗仗於奉天門外之東西。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0019",
          "zh": "龍旗十二，分左右，用甲士十二人。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0020",
          "zh": "北斗旗一、纛一居前，豹尾一居後，俱用甲 士三人。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0021",
          "zh": "虎豹各二，馴象六，分左右。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0022",
          "zh": "布旗六十四：門旗、日旗、月旗，青龍、 白虎、風、雲、雷、雨、江、河、淮、濟旗，天馬、天祿、白澤、朱雀、玄武等 旗，木、火、土、金、水五星旗，五嶽旗，熊旗，鸞旗及二十八宿旗，各六行；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0023",
          "zh": "每旗用甲士五人，一人執旗，四人執弓弩。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0024",
          "zh": "設五輅於奉天門外：玉輅居中，左金 輅，次革輅，右象輅，次木輅，俱並列。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0025",
          "zh": "丹墀左右布黃麾仗、黃蓋、華蓋、曲蓋、 紫方傘、紅方傘、雉扇、朱團扇、羽葆幢、豹尾、龍頭竿、信幡、傳教幡、告止 幡、絳引幡、戟氅、戈氅、儀鍠氅等，各三行。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0026",
          "zh": "丹陛左右陳幢節、響節、金節、 燭籠、青龍白虎幢、班劍、吾杖、立瓜、臥瓜、儀刀、鐙杖、戟、骨朵、朱雀玄 武幢等，各三行。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0027",
          "zh": "殿門左右設圓蓋一、金交椅、金腳踏、水盆、水罐、團黃扇、 紅扇。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0028",
          "zh": "皆校尉擎執。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0029",
          "zh": "洪武元年十月，定元旦朝賀儀：金吾衛於奉天門外分設旗幟。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0030",
          "zh": "宿衛於午門外 分設兵仗。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0031",
          "zh": "衛尉寺於奉天殿門及丹陛、丹墀設黃麾仗。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0032",
          "zh": "內使監擎執於殿上。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0033",
          "zh": "凡遇 冬至、聖節、冊拜、親王及蕃使來朝，儀俱同。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0034",
          "zh": "其宣詔赦、降香，則惟設奉天殿 門及丹陛儀仗、殿上擎執云。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0035",
          "zh": "其陳布次第，午門外，刀、盾、殳、叉各置於東西， 甲士用赤。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0036",
          "zh": "奉天門外中道，金吾、宿衛二衛設龍旗十二，分左右，用青甲士十二 人。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0037",
          "zh": "北斗旗一、纛一居前，豹尾一居後，俱用黑甲士三人。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0038",
          "zh": "虎豹各二，馴象六， 分左右。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0039",
          "zh": "左右布旗六十四：左前第一行，門旗二，每旗用紅甲士五人，內一人執 旗，旗下四人執弓箭。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0040",
          "zh": "第二行，月旗一，用白甲士五人，內一人執旗，旗下四人 執弩；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0041",
          "zh": "青龍旗一，用青甲士五人，內一人執旗，旗下四人執弩。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0042",
          "zh": "第三行，風、雲、 雷、雨旗各一，每旗用黑甲士五人，內一人執旗，旗下四人執弓箭；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0043",
          "zh": "天馬、白澤、 朱雀旗各一，每旗用紅甲士五人，內一人執旗，旗下四人執弓箭。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0044",
          "zh": "第四行，木、 火、土、金、水五星旗各一，隨其方色，每旗用甲士五人，內一人執旗，旗下四 人執弩，其甲木青、火紅、土黃、金白、水黑、熊旗、鸞旗各一，每旗用紅甲士 五人，內一人執旗，旗下四人執弩。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0045",
          "zh": "第五行角、亢、氐、房、心、尾、箕旗各一， 每旗用青甲士五人，內一人執旗，旗下四人執弓箭。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0046",
          "zh": "第六行鬥、牛、女、虛、危、 室、壁旗各一，每旗用青甲士五人，內一人執旗，旗下四人執弩。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0047",
          "zh": "右前第一行， 門旗二，每旗用紅甲士五人，內一人執旗，旗下四人執弓箭。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0048",
          "zh": "第二行，日旗一， 用紅甲士五人，內一人執旗，旗下四人執弩；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0049",
          "zh": "白虎旗一，用白甲士五人，內一人 執旗，旗下四人執弩。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0050",
          "zh": "第三行，江、河、淮、濟旗各一，隨其方色，每旗用甲士 五人，內一人執旗，旗下四人執弓箭，其甲江紅、河白、淮青、濟黑；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0051",
          "zh": "天祿、白 澤、玄武旗各一，每旗用甲士五人，內一人執旗，旗下四人執弓箭，天祿、白澤 紅甲，玄武黑甲。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0052",
          "zh": "第四行，東、南、中、西、北五嶽旗各一，隨其方色，每旗用 甲士五人，內一人執旗，旗下四人執弩，其甲東嶽青、南嶽紅、中嶽黃、西嶽白、 北嶽黑；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0053",
          "zh": "熊旗、麟旗各一，每旗用紅甲士五人，內一人執旗，旗下四人執弩。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0054",
          "zh": "第 五行，奎、婁、胃、昴、畢、觜、參旗各一，每旗用青甲士五人，內一人執旗， 旗下四人執弓箭。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0055",
          "zh": "第六行，井、鬼、柳、星、張、翼、軫旗各一，每旗用青甲士 五人，內一人執旗，旗下四人執弩。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0056",
          "zh": "奉天門外，拱衛司設五輅。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0057",
          "zh": "玉輅居中；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0058",
          "zh": "左金 輅，次革輅；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0059",
          "zh": "右象輅，次木輅。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0060",
          "zh": "俱並列。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0061",
          "zh": "典牧所設乘馬於文武樓之南，各三，東 西相向。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0062",
          "zh": "丹墀左右布黃麾仗凡九十，分左右，各三行。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0063",
          "zh": "左前第一行，十五：黃蓋 一，紅大傘二，華蓋一，曲蓋一，紫方傘一，紅方傘一，雉扇四，朱團扇四。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0064",
          "zh": "第 二行，十五：羽葆幢二，豹尾二，龍頭竿二，信幡二，傳教幡二，告止幡二，絳 引幡二，黃麾一。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0065",
          "zh": "第三行，十五：戟氅五，戈氅五，儀鍠氅五。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0066",
          "zh": "右前第一行，十 五：黃蓋一，紅大傘二，華蓋一，曲蓋一，紫方傘一，紅方傘一，雉扇四，朱團 扇四。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0067",
          "zh": "第二行，十五：羽葆幢二，豹尾二，龍頭竿二，信幡二，傳教幡二，告止 幡二，絳引幡二，黃麾一。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0068",
          "zh": "第三行，十五：戟氅五，戈氅五，儀鍠氅五。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0069",
          "zh": "皆校尉 擎執。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0070",
          "zh": "丹陛左右，拱衛司陳幢節等仗九十，分左右，爲四行。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0071",
          "zh": "左前第一行，響節 十二，金節三，燭籠三。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0072",
          "zh": "第二行，青龍幢一，班劍三，吾杖三，立瓜三，臥瓜三， 儀刀三，鐙杖三，戟三，骨朵三，朱雀幢一。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0073",
          "zh": "右前第一行，響節十二，金節三， 燭籠三。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0074",
          "zh": "第二行，白虎幢一，班劍三，吾杖三，立瓜三，臥瓜三，儀刀三，鐙杖 三，戟三，骨朵三，玄武幢一。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0075",
          "zh": "皆校尉擎執。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0076",
          "zh": "奉天殿門左右，拱衛司陳設：左行， 圓蓋一，金腳踏一，金水盆一，團黃扇三，紅扇三；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0077",
          "zh": "右行，圓蓋一，金交椅一， 金水罐一，團黃扇三，紅扇三。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0078",
          "zh": "皆校尉擎執。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0079",
          "zh": "殿上左右內使監陳設：左，拂子二， 金唾壺一，金香合一；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0080",
          "zh": "右，拂子二，金唾盂一，金香爐一。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0081",
          "zh": "皆內使擎執。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0082",
          "zh": "和聲郎 陳樂於丹墀文武官拜位之南，其器數詳見《樂志》內。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0083",
          "zh": "三年，命制郊丘祭祀拜褥。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0084",
          "zh": "郊丘用席表蒲裏爲褥，宗廟、社稷、先農、山川 用紅文綺表紅木棉布裏爲褥。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0085",
          "zh": "十二年，命禮部增設丹墀儀仗，黃傘、華蓋、曲蓋、 紫方傘、紅方傘各二，雉扇、紅團扇各四，羽葆幢、龍頭竿、絳引、傳教、告止、 信幡各六，戟氅、戈氅、儀鍠氅各十。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0086",
          "zh": "永樂元年，禮部言鹵簿中宜有九龍車一乘，請增置。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0087",
          "zh": "帝曰：「禮貴得中，過 爲奢，不及爲儉，先朝審之精矣。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0088",
          "zh": "當遵用舊章，豈可輒有增益，以啓後世之奢哉？",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0089",
          "zh": "九龍車既先朝所無，其仍舊便。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0090",
          "zh": "」宣德元年，更造鹵簿儀仗，有具服幄殿一座， 金交椅一，金腳踏一，金盆一，金罐一，金馬杌一，鞍籠一，金香爐一，金香合 一，金唾盂一，金唾壺一，御杖二，擺錫明甲一百副，盔一百，弓一百，箭三千， 刀一百。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0091",
          "zh": "其執事校尉，每人鵝帽，只孫衣，銅帶靴履鞋一副。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0092",
          "zh": "常朝，各色羅掌扇 四十，各色羅絹傘十，萬壽傘一，黃雙龍扇二。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0093",
          "zh": "筵宴，銷金羅傘四，銷金雨傘四， 金龍響節二十四。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0094",
          "zh": "皇太子儀仗，洪武元年定：門外中道設龍旗六，其執龍旗者並戎服。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0095",
          "zh": "黃旗一 居中，左前青旗一，右前赤旗一，左後黑旗一，右後白旗一，每旗執弓弩軍士六 人，服各隨旗色。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0096",
          "zh": "殿下設三十六人：絳引幡二，戟氅六，戈氅六，儀鍠氅六，羽 葆幢六，青方傘二，青小方扇四，青雜花團扇四，皆校尉擎執。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0097",
          "zh": "殿前設四十八人： 班劍四，吾杖四，立瓜四，臥瓜四，儀刀四，鐙杖四，骨朵四，斧四，響節十二， 金節四，皆校尉擎執。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0098",
          "zh": "殿門設十二人：金交椅一，金腳踏一，金水罐一，金水盆 一，青羅團扇六，紅圓蓋二，皆校尉擎執。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0099",
          "zh": "殿上設六人：金香爐一，香合一，唾 盂一，唾壺一，拂子二，皆內使擎執。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0100",
          "zh": "永樂二年，禮部言，東宮儀仗，有司失紀 載，視親王差少，宜增制金香爐、金香合各一，殳二，叉二，傳教、告止、信幡 各二，節二，幢二，夾槊二，槊、刀、盾各二十，戟八，紅紙油燈籠六，紅羅銷 金邊圓傘、紅羅繡圓傘各一，紅羅曲蓋繡傘、紅羅素圓傘、紅羅素方傘、青羅素 方傘各二，紅羅繡孔雀方扇、紅羅繡四季花團扇各四，拂子二，唾盂、唾壺各一， 鞍籠一，誕馬八，紅令旗二，清道旗四，幰弩一，白澤旗二，弓箭二十副。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0101",
          "zh": "從 之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0102",
          "zh": "親王儀仗，洪武六年定：宮門外設方色旗二，青色白澤旗二，執人服隨旗色， 並戎服。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0103",
          "zh": "殿下，絳引幡二，戟氅二，戈氅二，儀鍠氅二，皆校尉執。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0104",
          "zh": "殿前，班劍 二，吾杖二，立瓜二，臥瓜二，儀刀二，鐙杖二，骨朵二，斧二，響節八，皆校 尉執。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0105",
          "zh": "殿門，交椅一，腳踏一，水罐一，水盆一，團扇四，蓋二，皆校尉執。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0106",
          "zh": "殿 上，拂子二，香爐一，香合一，唾壺一，唾盂一。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0107",
          "zh": "十六年詔，親王儀仗內交椅、 盆、罐用銀者，悉改用金。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0108",
          "zh": "建文四年，禮部言，親王儀仗合增紅油絹銷金雨傘一， 紅紗燈籠、紅油紙燈籠各四，敔燈二，大小銅角四。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0109",
          "zh": "從之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0110",
          "zh": "永樂三年命工部，親 王儀仗內紅銷金傘，仍用寶珠龍文。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0111",
          "zh": "凡世子儀仗同。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0112",
          "zh": "郡王儀仗：令旗二，清道旗二，幰弩一，刀盾十六，弓箭十八副，絳引、 傳教、告止、信幡各二，吾杖、儀刀、立瓜、臥瓜、骨朵、斧各二，戟十六，槊 十六，麾一，幢一，節一，響節六，紅銷金圓傘一，紅圓傘一，紅曲柄傘二，紅 方傘二，青圓扇四，紅圓扇四，誕馬四，鞍籠一，馬杌一，拂子二，交椅一，腳 踏一，水盆一，水罐一，香爐一，紅紗燈籠二，敔燈二，帳房一座。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0113",
          "zh": "皇妃儀仗：紅杖二，清道旗二，絳引幡二，戈氅、戟氅、儀鍠氅、吾杖、儀 刀、班劍、立瓜、臥瓜、鐙杖、骨朵、金鉞各二，響節四，青方傘四，紅繡圓傘 一，繡方扇四，紅花圓扇四，青繡圓扇四，交椅一，腳踏一，拂子二，水盆一， 水罐一，香爐一，香合一，唾盂一，唾壺一，紅紗燈籠四。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0114",
          "zh": "東宮妃儀仗：紅杖二，清道旗二，絳引幡二，儀鍠氅、戈氅、戟氅、吾杖、 儀刀、班劍、立瓜、臥瓜、鐙杖、骨朵、金鉞各二，響節四，青方傘二，紅素圓 傘二，紅繡圓傘一，紅繡方扇四，紅繡花圓扇四，青繡圓扇四，交椅一，腳踏一， 拂子二，水盆一，水罐一，香爐一，香合一，紅紗燈籠四。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0115",
          "zh": "永樂二年，禮部言， 東宮妃儀仗如親王妃，惟香爐、香合如中宮，但亦不用金，其水盆、水罐皆用銀， 從之。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0116",
          "zh": "親王妃儀仗：紅杖二，清道旗二，絳引幡二，戟氅、吾杖、儀刀、班劍、立 瓜、臥瓜、骨朵、鐙杖各二，響節四，青方傘二，紅彩畫雲鳳傘一，青孔雀圓扇 四，紅花扇四，交椅一，腳踏一，水盆一，水罐一，紅紗燈籠四，拂子二。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0117",
          "zh": "公主、 世子妃儀仗俱同。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0118",
          "zh": "郡王妃儀仗：紅杖二，清道旗二，絳引幡二，戟氅、吾杖、班劍、立瓜、骨 朵各二，響節二，青方傘二，紅圓傘一，青圓扇二，紅圓扇二，交椅一，腳踏一， 拂子二，紅紗燈籠二，水盆一，水罐一。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0119",
          "zh": "郡主儀仗：紅杖二，清道旗二，班劍、吾杖、立瓜、骨朵各二，響節二，青 方傘一，紅圓傘一，青圓扇二，紅圓扇二，交椅一，腳踏一，水盆一，水罐一， 紅紗燈籠二，拂子二。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "sentences": [
        {
          "id": "s0120",
          "zh": "舊例，郡王儀仗有交椅、馬杌，皆木質銀裹；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0121",
          "zh": "水盆、水罐及香爐、香合，皆 銀質抹金；",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0122",
          "zh": "量折銀三百二十兩。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0123",
          "zh": "郡王妃儀仗，有交椅等大器，量折銀一百六十兩。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0124",
          "zh": "餘皆自備充用。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0125",
          "zh": "嘉靖四十四年定，除親王及親王妃初封儀仗照例頒給外，其初封 郡王及郡王妃折銀等項，並停止。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0126",
          "zh": "萬曆十年定，郡王初封系帝孫者，儀仗照例全 給，系王孫者免。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "s0127",
          "zh": "蓋宗室分封漸多，勢難遍給也。",
          "translations": [
            {
              "lang": "en",
              "literal": "",
              "idiomatic": "",
              "translator": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "translations": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "literal": "",
          "idiomatic": "",
          "translator": ""
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}